name: Surf
description: Surf AI is revolutionizing crypto research with specialized artificial intelligence that outperforms ChatGPT and Grok by 4x on cryptocurrency tasks. Fresh off a $15 million funding round from industry leaders Pantera Capital, Coinbase Ventures, and DCG, Surf combines real-time social sentiment, on-chain data across 40+ blockchains, and technical analysis to deliver institutional-grade research through a simple chat interface. With over 300,000 users and millions in annual revenue, Surf provides accurate, 'illusion-free' market intelligence that helps traders and investors navigate the complex crypto landscape with confidence.
